text = "An Enemy has a Preference for each Topic, which is either LIKE, NEUTRAL or DISLIKE.
Their reaction to your Topic Attacks varies based on their Preferences.
Is their Preference for a Topic NEUTRAL the CI Damage of your Dialogue stays unmodified.
Is it LIKE, CI Damage gets reduced by 1. Is it DISLIKE, CI Damage increases by 1.
If the Enemy’s Preference is LIKE or NEUTRAL, Topic Attacks also increase the Enthusiasm for this Topic by 1.
If the Enemy’s Preference is DISLIKE, the Annoyance of the Enemy will increase by 1."

