text = "Level of how enthusiastic the Enemy is for a Topic. High Levels of Enthusiasm generally prolong the Conversation, as it gradually raises the Conversation Interest Maximum.
Increasing Enthusiasm also increases the probability for the Enemy to use Dialogue for that Topic.
Enthusiasm increases when using Topic Dialogue on a Topic for which the Enemy’s Preference is either LIKE or NEUTRAL. Enemy Dialogue also increases Enthusiasm for that Topic.
Lowering Enthusiasm, will revert its effects like the raised Conversation Interest Maximum and increased probability. Lowering Enthusiasm is only possible through Dialogue Bonus Effects."

