text = "[ol]Every level of Enthusiasm raises Probability of the Enemy choosing Dialogue from the Topic they are enthusiastic for.
Starting with Level 2 Conversation Interest Maximum rises with every Level
Starting with Level 2 changing the Topic to a Topic with less than 2 Enthusiasm increases Annoyance by 1. Or by 2 Annoyance at Level 4.
Reaching Enthusiasm Level 3 or 5 lowers Annoyance by 1.
Starting at Level 4 the Enemy deals +1 MC Dmg with Dialogue for this Topic.
Successfully ending the Conversation with higher Levels of Enthusiasm grants a bonus to your Social Standing Change.
[/ol]"

