bbcode_enabled = true
text = "Level of how annoyed the Enemy is with you. Increasing Annoyance shortens the Conversation, as it gradually lowers Conversation Interest Maximum.
Annoyance increases by talking about Enemy DISLIKES, changing the Topic when the Enthusiasm is high or through Dialogue Bonus Effects.
But be careful, since reaching Annoyance Level 5 instantly ends the Conversation with similar effects to Mental Capacity reaching 0. Additionally every Level of Annoyance at the end of the Conversation lowers your Social Standing.
Seeing your Enemy getting annoyed is not pleasant. Raising Annoyance also costs you Social Battery. Also, knowingly increasing Annoyance costs 1 Social Battery.
(e.g. Using Topic Dialogue on a Topic for which you don’t know yet, that the Enemy has a DISLIKE, does not cost the additional 1 Social Battery)"

